for i in GroupI_specific_bins:
    conected_genes=bins_to_genes_assignments[bins_to_genes_assignments['id']==i]['connected_gene'].values
    if len(conected_genes)>0:
        for gene in conected_genes[0].split(','):
            linked_genes_name['GroupI'].add(gene)
    else:
        continue

for i in GroupII_specific_bins:
    conected_genes=bins_to_genes_assignments[bins_to_genes_assignments['id']==i]['connected_gene'].values
    if len(conected_genes)>0:
        for gene in conected_genes[0].split(','):
            linked_genes_name['GroupII'].add(gene)
    else:
        continue

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

import scipy.stats

import networkx as nx

def create_circular_pos(start,end,num_of_pos=10):
    theta=np.linspace(start,end,num_of_pos)
    x=np.cos(theta)
    y=np.sin(theta)
    return [(i,j) for i,j in zip(x,y)]

    pos[v]=p
    
for v,p in zip(list(GI_bins),create_circular_pos(12*np.pi/10,18*np.pi/10,len(GI_bins))):
    pos[v]=p    

for v,p in zip(list(GI_genes|GII_genes),np.linspace(-1,1,len(list(GI_genes)+list(GII_genes)))):
    pos[v]=(p,0)
    
node_colors=[]
for i in G.nodes():
    if i in GI_bins:
        node_colors.append('sandybrown')
    elif i in GII_bins:
        node_colors.append('blueviolet')
    else:
        node_colors.append('red')
edge_colors=[]
for i,j in G.edges():
    if i in GI_bins:
        edge_colors.append('sandybrown')
    elif i in GII_bins:
        edge_colors.append('blueviolet')
        
        
nx.draw(G,pos=pos,node_color=node_colors,edge_color=edge_colors,node_size=100)

plt.legend(handles=[plt.scatter([],[],c='red',label='Cell cycle genes',s=100),
                    plt.scatter([],[],c='sandybrown',label='GI-specific distal enhancers',s=100),
                    plt.scatter([],[],c='blueviolet',label='GII-speciifc distal enhancers',s=100)],
